Package gov.nasa.pds.objectAccess.table

Class DefaultFieldAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.pds.objectAccess.table.DefaultFieldAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FieldAdapter
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NumericTextFieldAdapter
    public class DefaultFieldAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements FieldAdapter
    Implements an adapter object for table fields that can read the field value from a byte array or write the field value into a byte array. Also has methods for formatting the value into an output writer for either delimited or fixed-width output. Methods not appropriate for the field type will throw UnsupportedOperationException.
